item.title: About
item.description: I am a biological sciences student that is focused, driven, and highly ambitious. I am empathetic and work extremely well in a team environment. I am very professional with aspirations to enter the field of Public Health with a focus on research and development. I plan to complete my Bachelor of Science degree in Neuroscience in the spring of 2020 at the University of Illinois - Chicago.
